=== Variance

Quantifies the spread or dispersion of a set of data points in a dataset

- Population

$
sigma^2 = 1/N sum_(i=1)^n (x_i - mu)^2
$

- Sample

$
s^2 = 1/(n - 1) sum_(i=1)^n (x_i - overline(x))^2
$

